claim: Flublok contains 45 micrograms (mcg) of HA per strain vs 15 mcg of HA per strain in a standard-dose influenza vaccine.
explanation: The image shows the cover header of a CDC MMWR (Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report) with the title, volume and issue number, and date, without any vaccine composition details. does not support the claim because the image only displays the report cover and does not include any information about hemagglutinin content per strain for Flublok or standard-dose influenza vaccines.
